{"tid":1668512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(戰術post)香港市區三大大遊行路線","createTime":"2019-10-22T04:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T19:10:38.000Z","uid":37804,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe425cc9686d64dd866fb4f6fdb464dc424fd9c","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"有見今次九龍大遊行反應不錯，引起小弟一啲反思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留意到啲重點想同大家分享<br />\n<br />\n首先，路線必須要係香港嘅經濟命脈，可以達成攬炒之效亦可以將我哋嘅思想宣傳俾更多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三條路線分別係:<br />\n港島 由中環行軒尼斯道至銅鑼灣<br />\n九龍 由尖沙咀行彌敦道至旺角<br />\n新界 沙田區，但我唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次就係起點同終點，套用返今次九龍大遊行就會明白點解港島大遊行次次都損兵折將，就係因為終點好多時係金鐘，行完又無車走，附近淨係得大路少橫街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點解我哋唔由中環開始行去銅鑼灣呢？<br />\n一來可以癱瘓中環至銅鑼灣租金最貴一帶<br />\n二來銅鑼灣交通方便<br />\n三來灣仔至銅鑼灣一帶有橫街同天橋<br />\n四來每次行到金鐘再被趕返去銅鑼灣體力都有消耗<br />\n<br />\n至於九龍路線可以由尖沙咀一路至旺角，原因都係一樣，而新界沙田就唔係好熟，希望有巴絲可以提供意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以推上熱門令更多人一齊討論吓，我個人就認為可以每周末三區不停輪流大遊行，跨區時就做和理派，本區時就做勇武派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps:大西北屯元天嗰邊真係完全唔熟，如果有巴絲有idea都歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e62f42cd8b8efb7e80378bb6b98edf3579fcf41","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"90e66548456d83af1803aba776fd4e1821ca0677","tid":1668512,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸出革命文宣圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/akqjfDV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/akqjfDV</a>"},{"pid":"fe563075378a8b68e32efdd417d8a77c845d1bf0","tid":1668512,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"「重要」《香港獨立與加泰羅尼亞獨立 - 需保持距離》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668486</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f7a46a9e00a458250b2f7d3f05b998b6fb2343f","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874fb8b23c6716bb05807495f64ca83c6d5dbda2","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6e5a35510ddf681e6d1ad9e423894342fd6f65","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"自pish一下"},{"pid":"2075c01128bf5842e4af11b917529f67cf69d9a3","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自pish"},{"pid":"a45a1397bffa90413cc4540fe2b23da4ac312c56","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"自pish 1"},{"pid":"e833f453b87d6109cde4f9b5845d9f2cea985b50","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"自pish 2"},{"pid":"0cba973f469f3b3834d5a4ddb25d82419f14ce9f","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"自pish 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb80fb1a8c73f480604ef7c5d915f556561512f","tid":1668512,"uid":97979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"幫你pish下"},{"pid":"fffe7e2b02d63d57a998c7c67f6c2722c1996fab","tid":1668512,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"屌 銅鑼灣天后次次俾人圍捕"},{"pid":"2f44ba9be6458e4e18348a1b8ec85de6c6b16c01","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fffe7e2b02d63d57a998c7c67f6c2722c1996fab","tid":1668512,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"屌 銅鑼灣天后次次俾人圍捕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:35:50.000Z","msg":"所以我先諗覺得係起點終點方向嘅問題，油尖旺區其實佢哋都可以圍我哋，但因為旺角方向有和理人士幫我哋確保退路我哋先容易走<br />\n<br />\n同樣如果隊頭係向銅鑼灣，係咪可以做到同樣效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56582b717004b9bd2ed41f073bd822b74cae79aa","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fffe7e2b02d63d57a998c7c67f6c2722c1996fab","tid":1668512,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"屌 銅鑼灣天后次次俾人圍捕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:38:15.000Z","msg":"我都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我留意到4個月來真係無將條路線調轉過，加上軒尼斯道有好多天橋可以做制高點，但我哋每次隊頭向金鐘就會去咗警總天橋開戰，好不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dae476d37fca003807bf34b3b640adc7c50c4b","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fb80fb1a8c73f480604ef7c5d915f556561512f","tid":1668512,"uid":97979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"幫你pish下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"感謝你啊，唔知我有無講得1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553d42329ae9aa7d1840f9cd76d8dfe3981e57ba","tid":1668512,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:44:16.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣去北角咪得囉，要由頭到尾都近內街"},{"pid":"c6e6b0e4a225d38c5bf1bf2495437f316de1968d","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"553d42329ae9aa7d1840f9cd76d8dfe3981e57ba","tid":1668512,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:44:16.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣去北角咪得囉，要由頭到尾都近內街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:46:04.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠影響經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最貴地段好似由中環開始"},{"pid":"e5c7349a46075c5e782e2dd1284762e1f58a3320","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:48:39.000Z","msg":"差唔多瞓，重點就係留意返尖沙咀都係死位，但調轉行就無事<br />\n<br />\n相反港島遊行路線永遠都無轉過方向，不停向金鐘中環死位行"},{"pid":"ad137b8ae730c235a13652db33c4acb32180d450","tid":1668512,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6e6b0e4a225d38c5bf1bf2495437f316de1968d","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"553d42329ae9aa7d1840f9cd76d8dfe3981e57ba","tid":1668512,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:44:16.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣去北角咪得囉，要由頭到尾都近內街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:46:04.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠影響經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最貴地段好似由中環開始"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣至北角起碼多街口易打遊擊<br />\n另沙田條路線都可以傾下<br />\n另開多條大西北我都贊成<br />\n4條應該都好夠做"},{"pid":"d6cf99d7d5989b4f9b56654e13930d3956da5b51","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad137b8ae730c235a13652db33c4acb32180d450","tid":1668512,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6e6b0e4a225d38c5bf1bf2495437f316de1968d","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"553d42329ae9aa7d1840f9cd76d8dfe3981e57ba","tid":1668512,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:44:16.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣去北角咪得囉，要由頭到尾都近內街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:46:04.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠影響經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最貴地段好似由中環開始"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣至北角起碼多街口易打遊擊<br />\n另沙田條路線都可以傾下<br />\n另開多條大西北我都贊成<br />\n4條應該都好夠做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:51:49.000Z","msg":"4條主要命脈就最好，不過銅鑼灣之後得小店，啲租金唔夠貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中環啲租，停一日都爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7603621c1a9428c75eab91e43b7242818f0f5101","tid":1668512,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZmVAJh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZmVAJh.gif&h=e039eabd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2da645671dd5a970430e64f68e4c06bfc3e6a611","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7603621c1a9428c75eab91e43b7242818f0f5101","tid":1668512,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZmVAJh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZmVAJh.gif&h=e039eabd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:11:13.000Z","msg":"好正好得意啊"},{"pid":"ccff200429bc61c8df8e137946601beed93d203e","tid":1668512,"uid":137156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:22:06.000Z","msg":"沙田遊行舊路線真係唔太好<br />\n終點係到火車站，個度唔經狗鐵係無得散<br />\n即係遊行至中途沙田路線基本上停擺或者唔經沙田<br />\n因為遊行後必封沙燕橋兩個十字路口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者睇下行遠啲到大圍或乙明、沙田圍仲有無巴士站未停<br />\n加上沙田同田心狗屋支援真係五至十分鐘嘅事<br />\n沙田狗屋都加重咗防架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申都唔多熟沙田，係依排重溫緊依四個月大事回顧"},{"pid":"f54c59f92a6dfec9cf7204dd539ae847a59baaac","tid":1668512,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣嚟講 上次班狗守維園同sogo <br />\n已經大致封死東行撤退路線<br />\n而西行係去金鐘仲衰<br />\n<br />\n比較上灣仔同中環都多啲位走"},{"pid":"2c6beca0a2aff2b0549d0086495619c449f1c1d4","tid":1668512,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:36:48.000Z","msg":"東沙田大埔<br />\n<br />\n西屯門元朗(商場做據點)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1351b5dc96b36e1a91446ee21157d97e6355c01","tid":1668512,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe425cc9686d64dd866fb4f6fdb464dc424fd9c","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"有見今次九龍大遊行反應不錯，引起小弟一啲反思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留意到啲重點想同大家分享<br />\n<br />\n首先，路線必須要係香港嘅經濟命脈，可以達成攬炒之效亦可以將我哋嘅思想宣傳俾更多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三條路線分別係:<br />\n港島 由中環行軒尼斯道至銅鑼灣<br />\n九龍 由尖沙咀行彌敦道至旺角<br />\n新界 沙田區，但我唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次就係起點同終點，套用返今次九龍大遊行就會明白點解港島大遊行次次都損兵折將，就係因為終點好多時係金鐘，行完又無車走，附近淨係得大路少橫街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點解我哋唔由中環開始行去銅鑼灣呢？<br />\n一來可以癱瘓中環至銅鑼灣租金最貴一帶<br />\n二來銅鑼灣交通方便<br />\n三來灣仔至銅鑼灣一帶有橫街同天橋<br />\n四來每次行到金鐘再被趕返去銅鑼灣體力都有消耗<br />\n<br />\n至於九龍路線可以由尖沙咀一路至旺角，原因都係一樣，而新界沙田就唔係好熟，希望有巴絲可以提供意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以推上熱門令更多人一齊討論吓，我個人就認為可以每周末三區不停輪流大遊行，跨區時就做和理派，本區時就做勇武派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps:大西北屯元天嗰邊真係完全唔熟，如果有巴絲有idea都歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:44:43.000Z","msg":"其實一直都講應該係中環行返去銅鑼灣, 我都唔知點解硬係要掉轉. 銅鑼灣散水易好多"},{"pid":"821dae85727bf0c51be934c29a20361378e87c44","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c6beca0a2aff2b0549d0086495619c449f1c1d4","tid":1668512,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:36:48.000Z","msg":"東沙田大埔<br />\n<br />\n西屯門元朗(商場做據點)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:59:10.000Z","msg":"兩邊都唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點行好?"},{"pid":"7b58afaea2a87f8b208e6ff28450823ae276d014","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccff200429bc61c8df8e137946601beed93d203e","tid":1668512,"uid":137156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:22:06.000Z","msg":"沙田遊行舊路線真係唔太好<br />\n終點係到火車站，個度唔經狗鐵係無得散<br />\n即係遊行至中途沙田路線基本上停擺或者唔經沙田<br />\n因為遊行後必封沙燕橋兩個十字路口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者睇下行遠啲到大圍或乙明、沙田圍仲有無巴士站未停<br />\n加上沙田同田心狗屋支援真係五至十分鐘嘅事<br />\n沙田狗屋都加重咗防架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申都唔多熟沙田，係依排重溫緊依四個月大事回顧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"新城市行去大圍 易唔易散?"},{"pid":"b071dc488c5c4670043ebc1d5436cc6346d05249","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f54c59f92a6dfec9cf7204dd539ae847a59baaac","tid":1668512,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣嚟講 上次班狗守維園同sogo <br />\n已經大致封死東行撤退路線<br />\n而西行係去金鐘仲衰<br />\n<br />\n比較上灣仔同中環都多啲位走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"我知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實隊頭人數會多啲，混入其中都走到<br />\n係咪要pm民陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900bb3ae1decf3e018a261a933afee0d9c6a973a","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"自pish 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b080fd501cab8989278f7e6a1f2873bdbb9465","tid":1668512,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply